nodes.text: Ohali Two was a female Duros clone, created by Marvid and Craitheus Qreph of Jedi Knight Ohali Soroc aboard Base Prime, Han Solo nicknamed Ditto. She was mentally deficient due to imperfections from Force-sensitive cloning. Ohali Two was killed by a stray laser bolt when Solo, working with Barduun, made his attempt to escape the Qrephs' clutches.
